# UI Theme Rules

## Theme

- Primary theme name: `bankcore`
- DaisyUI provides tokens; product identity comes from custom theme values
- Dark shell, light workspace (not fully dark)

## Semantic Tokens

- `primary` → commit actions, selected nav
- `success` → posted, in-balance, complete
- `warning` → pending review, override needed
- `error` → invalid, failed, out-of-balance

## Reference

See `docs/00_initial_core_references/tailwind_daisyui_theme_spec.md` for full token mapping and class guidance.
